                  Decorative designs:
                  <locus target="#1r #13v #20r #40r #48v #72r #105r"/> (haräg)
                  <locus target="#7r"/> (multiple full stops and a line of alternating red and black dots);
                  <locus target="#84r"/> (line of red and black dots)
                </decoNote>
